name: CMMagneticFieldCalibrationAccuracy
desc: Indicates the calibration accuracy of a magnetic field estimate

items.name: case uncalibrated
items.desc: The magnetic field estimate is not calibrated.

items.name: case low
items.desc: The accuracy of the magnetic field calibration is low.

items.name: case medium
items.desc: The accuracy of the magnetic field calibration is medium.

items.name: case high
items.desc: The accuracy of the magnetic field calibration is high.
